    "verses": [
      {
        "verse": "1",
        "text": "In days of Ahaz son of Jotham, son of Uzziah, king of Judah, Rezin king of Syria and Pekah son of Remaliah king of Israel went up to Jerusalem to war, but couldn’t conquer it."
